org.eclipse.viatra.integration.mwe2

Interface IMessageFactory<ParameterType,Message extends IMessage<ParameterType>>

  • Type Parameters:
    ParameterType - Type of the parameter of the messages to be created.
    Message - Type of the messages to be created.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StringMessageFactory

    public interface IMessageFactory<ParameterType,Message extends IMessage<ParameterType>>
    Interface that defines the base functions of a message factory. These factories are responsible for the creation of certain typed messages. The type of these messages is specified in the template parameter, while the parameter type of these messages is specified in the template parameter.
